author: Steven Lemongello
title: Trump expected to stop in Melbourne Saturday
text:
Trump expected to stop in Melbourne Saturday Donald Trump Orlando Sentinel Orlando Sentinel Steven Lemongello is expected to make a stop in Melbourne Saturday as part of his weekend trip to Florida, Brevard County spokesman Don Walker said.
Walker said he was told by the White House that Trump’s plane would be stopping at Orlando Melbourne International Airport Saturday as he makes his way down to Mar-a-Lago in Palm Beach, the third visit in as many weeks to what the Trump administration calls the “Winter White House.” 
Walker said he did not know what time Trump would be at the airport or whether there would be any public event. He said the White House was still working out details.
